  "title": "Jr Brand Marketing Crew – Join ASAP! Work with Friends!",
  "description": "<p><strong>🎉 Fun Brand Marketing Crew – Join ASAP!</strong></p>\n<p><br>\n <em>Work with Friends | No Experience Needed | Fresh Grads Welcome!</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ready to kickstart your career in a fun, energetic environment? We’re looking for lively, outgoing individuals to join our <strong>Brand Marketing Crew</strong> — where work feels more like a good time with great people!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong><br>\n Represent brands at events, roadshows &amp; pop-ups<br>\n Help the team hit campaign goals (and celebrate wins!)<br>\n Create fun, memorable experiences </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why You’ll Love It:</strong><br>\n✅ Work with your friends (yes!)<br>\n✅ Immediate start, training provided<br>\n✅ Fixed hours + fixed schedule options<br>\n✅ Young, friendly team with great vibes<br>\n✅ Incentives, growth opportunities &amp; daily fun!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>No experience? No problem. <br>\n<u><strong>📩 Apply now – the crew’s waiting for you!</strong></u></p>",
